<section xml:id="sec-safety" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Safety</title>

  <p> No Lab equipment can be used without proper safety training. 
    This information is included at orientation and training sessions. (see “Training” above) </p>

  <p>
    Each Lab is provided with the appropriate safety equipment, 
    first aid, and fire suppression appropriate for its machines and processes. 
  </p>

  <p>
    In the event of a severe injury or fire: 911 must be called and 
    Belhaven Security notified (601) 968-5900.
  </p>

</section>